init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see a tiny bee, no bigger than a quarter.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm sorry, your Majesty, I didn't mean to startle you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am a bee of the Royal Guard, and I am here to protect you, your Majesty."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look around, making sure no one is watching.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We are dangerous, your Majesty, but only to those who would harm you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Very well, your Majesty." said the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You stare at the bee for a moment, then start to laugh.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes, your Majesty." said the bee, not laughing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm not going anywhere with you." you say.
